    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in concours-level condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system. Power is managed by a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and delivered to the rear wheels via a 3.62:1 limited-slip differential. The chassis has been meticulously inspected for subframe integrity, with preventative reinforcement already performed. Mechanically flawless, the engine exhibits zero rod bearing play and maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders. Finished in pristine Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this M3 retains its original factory bushings and suspension geometry, offering the precise, analog feedback these Munich-born icons are celebrated for.",
